9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Dragon Ball Z: Bojack Unbound | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Mr. Money is holding another World Martial Arts Tournament and Mr. Satan invites everyone in the world to join in. Little does he know that Bojack, an ancient villain who has escaped his prison, is competing. Since Goku is currently dead, it is up to Gohan, Vegeta, and Trunks to defeat Bojack and his henchman."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106087/dragon-ball-z-bojack-unbound"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Dragon Ball Z: Bojack Unbound"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Mr. Money is holding another World Martial Arts Tournament and Mr. Satan invites everyone in the world to join in. Little does he know that Bojack, an ancient villain who has escaped his prison, is competing. Since Goku is currently dead, it is up to Gohan, Vegeta, and Trunks to defeat Bojack and his henchman."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106087/dragon-ball-z-bojack-unbound"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iihTK9Af8G1ZzBjkIIAV4qQMkzF.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Dragon Ball Z: Bojack Unbound"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Mr. Money is holding another World Martial Arts Tournament and Mr. Satan invites everyone in the world to join in. Little does he know that Bojack, an ancient villain who has escaped his prison, is competing. Since Goku is currently dead, it is up to Gohan, Vege